SHA_256

public static final MessageDigestAlgorithm SHA_256
SHA-256 hash algorithm defined in FIPS PUB 180-2. Intended to provide 128 bits of security against collision attacks.

SHA_384

public static final MessageDigestAlgorithm SHA_384
SHA-384 hash algorithm defined in FIPS PUB 180-2. Derived by truncating SHA-512 output.

SHA_512

public static final MessageDigestAlgorithm SHA_512
SHA-512 hash algorithm defined in FIPS PUB 180-2. Intended to provide 256 bits of security against collision attacks.
